<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    {{>upperlinks}}
    <title>Copy.ai</title>
</head>

<body>
    {{>nav}}
    <div class="intro">
        <h1>Copy.ai Text Generation</h1>
        <div class="read-word"></div>
        <div class="count-word"></div>
        <p>Using artificial intelligence (AI), the programme copy.ai creates high-quality content for a variety of tasks, including
        blog articles, product descriptions, and more.
        The programme analyses a lot of material to find patterns and common themes using sophisticated natural language
        processing (NLP) methods.
        It then makes use of this data to produce new content that is stylistically and grammatically close to the original.</p>
        <p>Copy.ai may help content authors save time and effort, which is one of its key advantages.
        Users only need to enter a few keywords or phrases, and the programme will create a high-quality piece of content in a
        matter of minutes, saving them from having to spend hours researching and creating new stuff.
        This is especially helpful for companies and people that frequently need to generate huge volumes of information.</p>
        <p>The ability to generate content that is SEO-friendly, or optimised for search engines like Google, is another advantage
        of Copy.ai.
        This can increase a website's exposure and make online information simpler for users to locate.</p>
        <p>The application also provides users with a range of customization options so they may modify the produced text to suit
        their particular requirements.
        Users can select from a variety of tone and style options, for instance, such as formal, casual, or amusing.
        Additionally, they may choose the text's length, which ranges from a few phrases to many pages.</p>
        <p>Copy.ai is simple to use and doesn't require any technical knowledge.
        The programme will produce the content for users if they just enter their keywords or phrases and their selected
        alternatives.
        The created text can then be utilised as is or changed as necessary.</p>
        <p>In conclusion, Copy.ai is an effective application that makes use of AI to produce excellent writing for a range of
        needs.
        It is a useful tool for organisations and people that need to effortlessly and rapidly publish big volumes of material
        due to its time-saving and customisation options.</p>
    </div>








    <script>
        const paragraphs = document.querySelectorAll(".intro p");
        const readTimeDiv = document.querySelector(".read-word");
        const count = document.querySelector(".count-word");

        const calculatedReadTime = () => {
            let numberOfWords = 0;
            const averageWPM = 265;

            paragraphs.forEach(paragraph => {
                numberOfWords += paragraph.innerHTML.split(" ").length;
            })

            let readTime = numberOfWords / averageWPM;

            readTimeDiv.innerHTML = Math.round(readTime) + " minute read"
            count.innerHTML = numberOfWords + " -words approximate"

        }
        calculatedReadTime();



    </script>

    {{>lowerlinks}}
</body>

</html>